style='font-size:26.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:white'>丁二红规则说明</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:宋体;color:white'><br>
</span><strong><span style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>牌型及大小说明</span></strong><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:宋体;color:white'><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>扯旋游戏使用<span lang=EN-US>32</span>张扑克牌，分别是：（非特殊说明，红代表红桃和方片，黑代表黑桃和梅花）红桃<span
lang=EN-US>3</span>（只有一张）、红<span lang=EN-US>2</span>、红<span lang=EN-US>Q</span>、大王、黑<span
lang=EN-US>5</span>、黑<span lang=EN-US>9</span>、黑<span lang=EN-US>J</span>以及<span
lang=EN-US>4</span>、<span lang=EN-US>6</span>、<span lang=EN-US>7</span>、<span
lang=EN-US>8</span>、<span lang=EN-US>10</span>各四张。涉及的牌型主要由两张牌组合而成。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style='font-family:宋体;
color:white'>其中<strong><span style='font-family:宋体'>单牌及大小顺序如下：红<span
lang=EN-US>Q</span>＞红<span lang=EN-US>2</span>＞红<span lang=EN-US>8</span>＞红<span
lang=EN-US>4</span>＞（黑<span lang=EN-US>10</span>＝黑<span lang=EN-US>4</span>＝黑<span
lang=EN-US>6</span>）＞（黑<span lang=EN-US>J</span>＝红<span lang=EN-US>10</span>＝红<span
lang=EN-US>6</span>＝红<span lang=EN-US>7</span>）＞（杂<span lang=EN-US>5</span>＝黑<span
lang=EN-US>7</span>＝黑<span lang=EN-US>8</span>＝杂<span lang=EN-US>9</span>＝红桃<span
lang=EN-US>3</span>＝大王）</span></strong>。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style='font-family:宋体;
color:white'>两张牌的大小顺序如下：丁二皇＞对天＞对地＞对人＞对和＞（对梅＝对长二＝对长三）＞（对斧头＝对四六＝对珠珠＝对幺六）＞对子＞天王＞地王＞天杠＞地杠＞天关九＞地关九＞人十九＞和五九＞（板五九＝丁长九＝梅十九）＞（丁珠九＝乌龙九＝苕十九）＞散牌。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:宋体;color:white'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style='font-family:宋体;
color:white'>特殊牌型：三花十、三花六：黑<span lang=EN-US>10</span>＋红<span
lang=EN-US>10</span>＋黑<span lang=EN-US>J</span>＋任一张牌称作三花十，黑<span lang=EN-US>6</span>＋红<span
lang=EN-US>6</span>＋大王＋任一张牌称作三花六，拿到三花十或者三花六的牌，则该局既不输也不赢。若不丢牌，则牌形失效。<span
lang=EN-US><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>如果不符合以上牌型，则按照牌面点数相加，取个位的点数，称为散牌，散牌中<span lang=EN-US>8</span>点最大，<span
lang=EN-US>0</span>点最小。其中红<span lang=EN-US>Q</span>是<span lang=EN-US>2</span>点，黑<span
lang=EN-US>J</span>是<span lang=EN-US>1</span>点，大王是<span lang=EN-US>6</span>点，其他为对应牌点。</span></p>

